  "description": "<i>Thrax Lair</i> is a vertical shoot'em-up, that kind of resembles River Raid.<br><br>Thrax, insect-like, cave-dwelling creatures, have always stolen the eggs from tarps and their offsprings. \nTarps are pterodactyl-size creatures that have the ability to shoot electro-chemical energy through its eyes.\nThis is a recreation of a tarp raid on a thrax lair.<br><br>You control up to 3 tarps and for every 10,000 points you score you awarded with an extra tarp.\nThe tarp can fire energy bursts from its eyes in the front direction, left, right, and the diagonal front directions.\nYou score points by shooting enemies. The faster you fly the more points you get. Depending on the kind of thrax you are awarded with more or less points:<br><br>Workers will give you 30 victory points.\nSoldiers will give you 75 victory points.\nStingers will give you 150 victory points.\nMonitors will give you 350 victory points. \nTo kill a Monitor or Stinger you have to hit the eyes.",
